				<wikidot:authorName>mayoculpa</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3489662</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>:D Huzzah! And thank you.</p> <p>That was the seed thought that started me down this road. In <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/upside-down-cake">Upside-Down Cake</a> he is genuinely surprised that his circus members aren't chomping at the bit to take each other down a peg. They view him as a cruel, overbearing tyrant, but he doesn't see himself that way - he thinks he's a laid-back, generally merciful guy.</p> <p>So I says to myself, I says, &quot;what does <em>normal</em> look like to a person like that?&quot;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
