						 <p>Woohoo! This was a tough one to write.</p> <p>Many thanks, as always, to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1698079&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1544245349" alt="Metaphysician" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1698079)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" >Metaphysician</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1544245349" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span> for canon congruency checkups, and DrChandra again for very helpful crits. Some great crits from <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1544245349" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span> helped me trim down the rambling a bit. I also got crits from <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1544245349" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span> (who, I must note, was strongly in favor of rambling) as well as <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2198340&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1544245349" alt="Kakroom" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2198340)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" >Kakroom</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ghostpage" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2567302&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1544245349" alt="ghostpage" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2567302)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ghostpage" >ghostpage</a></span>. (If you gave me crits and I missed you please let me know!)</p> <p>Although the Fullers live in Cambridge, to paraphrase Kakroom, this is indeed my take on &quot;Sarkic Southern hospitality.&quot;</p> <p>Edit: The next and last installment is outlined; I'll get to work on getting it drafted and up for crits shortly.</p> 
